[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "……真面目ですわね、あなたは。\n出会った時から変わらず",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00966",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "はは……\n社長殿にはたびたびご迷惑をおかけいたしました",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00967",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "うう……今月も苦しい……\nまたバイト増やさないと……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00968",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（っ！　事務所から……もしや仕事の依頼！？）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00969",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "はい！　……はい。はい……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00970",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "え……クビ……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00971",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "はあ……この先どうすれば……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00972",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "そこのあなた。少しいいかしら？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00973",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "は、はい？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00974",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "わたくし、こういう者です。\nあなたを我が社にスカウトしに来ましたわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00975",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "ララ・プロダクション……って、あの！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00976",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "鬼門さん。あなたが長らくアイドルとして芽が出ず、\n燻っていることは存じております",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00977",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "うう……そんなはっきり言わなくても",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00978",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "しかし、それを知っているならなにゆえ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00979",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "あなたにはアイドルの才能があります",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00980",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "芽が出ないのは、事務所の売り出し方に\n原因がある、とわたくしは分析しておりますわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00981",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "あなたがまだ夢を諦めていないのなら、\nわたくしについておいでなさいな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00982",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "あなた宛てのファンレター、\nそちらの箱にしまってありますわよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00983",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "おお！　って、やはり今回も１通だけですか……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00984",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "その送り主、以前も名前を見た記憶がありますわ。\n熱心なファンなのですね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00985",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "ええ、まあ。前の事務所にいた頃から、\nよく手紙をいただいておりまして",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00986",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "その熱意に報いるためにも、\n頑張らねばなりませぬ……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00987",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "その真面目さはあなたの長所ですわね。\nただ、アイドルとしては少々固すぎるかもしれません",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00988",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "う、それは拙者も自覚しておりますが……\n昔からの性分なものでして……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00989",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "むむむ……これも家の教えが古臭いせいでござる！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00990",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "ふむ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00991",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "それでは、ユニットを組んでみましょうか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00992",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "へ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00993",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "その真面目さはリーダー向きですわ。多少個性の強い\nメンバーでも、あなたならまとめられるはず",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00994",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "しゃ、社長殿！？　そんないきなり！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00995",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "そうと決まれば、早速メンバー探しといきましょう！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00996",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "お、お待ちくだされー！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00997",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "それからトントン拍子に話は進み、\nついには大きな舞台まで……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00998",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "このひと月……拙者にとっては\n夢のような時間でございまする",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00999",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "……寂しいですが、あなたの決めたことならば、\nわたくしは尊重いたしますわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_01000",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "年末のカウントダウンフェス……\n必ず成功させ、盛大に花道を飾りましょう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_01001",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "……はい！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01002",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]